OL,4,CBen Roberts, Derek Conway on The Bill,
OL,5,Cdies at 70
OL,6, Ben Roberts, best known for playing
OL,7, Chief Inspector Derek Conway in The
OL,8, Bill from 1987 to 2002, has died at 70.
OL,10,FHis death was confirmed by his former
OL,11,Fagent, who called him a "wonderful"
OL,12,Factor who had had "an extensive career
OL,13,Fin theatre, TV and film".
OL,15,FRoberts' character on the ITV police
OL,16,Fdrama was an an old-fashioned officer
OL,17,Fand a trained hostage negotiator.
OL,19,FConway was ultimately killed when a
OL,20,Fpetrol bomb was thrown into his panda
OL,21,Fcar.
